{"id":302,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/302","type":2,"name":"となりのトトロ","name_cn":"龙猫","summary":"本片是對日本鄉村生活的迷人及節奏緩慢的描繪。故事背景設定於1958年（昭和33年），一位大學教授和他的兩個女兒搬進一個森林附近的一所舊房子，因為他的妻子染上了結核病，在附近的一所醫院康復中。他的女兒們發現了「煤炭屎」，她們又名「煤炭屎鬼」。\r\n\r\n次子追趕一隻小龍貓，牠引領了她去找到森林守護者「龍貓」。次子被牠們迷住了，並且下定決心去尋找大龍貓。一個下雨的晚上，當女孩們在等爸爸時，她們遇到了一個，用樹葉擋雨的大龍貓。當次子想把一個成熟的玉米帶給住在醫院的媽媽時，但迷了路，草子到處尋找她，最後去找大龍貓幫忙。並且在牠的幫助下，梅被迅速找到了。龍貓召喚而來的貓公車，接送草子和次子穿過鄉間，到醫院探望她們的媽媽。","eps":[{"id":96816,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/96816","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"となりのトトロ","name_cn":"龙猫","duration":"88m","airdate":"1988-04-16","comment":4,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"1988-04-16","air_weekday":6,"rating":{"total":5673,"count":{"1":4,"2":0,"3":3,"4":13,"5":41,"6":205,"7":940,"8":2343,"9":1476,"10":648},"score":8.2},"rank":113,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/57/7b/302_zSSjC.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/57/7b/302_zSSjC.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/57/7b/302_zSSjC.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/57/7b/302_zSSjC.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/57/7b/302_zSSjC.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":609,"collect":8135,"doing":46,"on_hold":73,"dropped":18},"crt":[{"id":3582,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/3582","name":"草壁メイ","name_cn":"","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9d/68/3582_crt_anidb.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/9d/68/3582_crt_anidb.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/9d/68/3582_crt_anidb.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9d/68/3582_crt_anidb.jpg"},"comment":0,"collects":3,"info":{"gender":"女","alias":{"jp":"草壁メイ","romaji":"Kusakabe Mei"},"source":"anidb.net"},"actors":[{"id":4092,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/4092","name":"坂本千夏","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/77/34/4092_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/77/34/4092_seiyu_anidb.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/77/34/4092_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/77/34/4092_seiyu_anidb.jpg"}}]},{"id